/****************************************

Group Colors Instructions:

1. 7 pre-installed groups! Replace the color name with your own groupname (one word only).
2. Remember to change the prefix and suffix when installing your group! For example, for
group "peach" the prefix was  and the suffix was . Needed for
the name links to change color.
3. To add more group colors, copy the code below:

#g-4, .mg-groupname {
    --mg-color: #, #, #;
}
.mg-groupname {
	color: rgba(#, #, #, 1)
}

... replace 4 with the group id number and groupname with your groupname. Remember to use
rgb color format.

*****************************************/

